title: Trump says Kazakhstan joining Abraham Accords ‘first of many’ in second term

author: Molly Parks
description: A federal district court in Iowa ruled in favor of pollster Ann Selzer and the Des Moines Register on Tuesday, dismissing a lawsuit brought by a West Des Moines resident who sued the paper over a 2024 presidential poll that showed Kamala Harris poised to defeat President Donald Trump. title: District court dismisses class-action suit against Iowa pollster Ann Selzer
